@uk_domain_names Similar in Austria; scary actually.  Cases have increased as well, but the prospect of mandatory vaccinations has not led to more people getting their vaccinations. V. depressing.

Note: since the data above is based on the specimen collection date, it should be unaffected by the lack of reporting at weekends. That doesn't change when people took the tests, only when we are informed about the results.
